narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The project is a lot of work...if you don't have a senior thesis due second semester and have a light workload otherwise, it's a pretty good course to take.
The class is a lot of fun, and very rewarding. Even though it's really hard it's well worth it. Use each other as resources!
It's the senior project, kids! Professor Khalil is the chillest. Get pumped.
